XTerm icin sunlar:

    ~/.inputrc
    set meta-flag on
    set convert-meta off
    set output-meta on


    ~/.Xdefaults
    XTerm*metaSendsEscape: true
    XTerm*eightBitInput: false


UXTerm icin de /etc/X11/app-defaults/UXTerm dosyasina sunlari eklemek gerek:

    *metaSendsEscape: true
    *eightBitInput: false

